# PLEASE README !

We've successfully made the simple one client server multiple segments protocol.

And then to simulate the multiple clients, we just made the easier way by calling the fork() system call.

that duplicates the current process, creating a child process that runs concurrently with the parent process.

and this is the result of the multiple clients exchanging with the server.
